  "prompt": "What should a fresher expect from a company?",
  "response": "As a fresher, here are some expectations from a company:\n\n1. Learning Opportunities\n- Training programs\n- Mentorship\n- Skill development\n- Opportunities to learn new technologies\n\n2. Professional Work Environment\n- Supportive colleagues\n- Clear communication\n- Respectful workplace culture\n- Basic infrastructure and tools\n\n3. Compensation\n- Competitive entry-level salary\n- Performance-based increments\n- Transparency in compensation structure\n\n4. Career Growth\n- Clear career path\n- Regular performance reviews\n- Potential for internal promotions\n- Exposure to different projects\n\n5. Work-Life Balance\n- Reasonable working hours\n- Flexible work arrangements\n- Leave policies\n- Health benefits\n\n6. Onboarding Support\n- Structured induction program\n- Introduction to company processes\n- Initial handholding\n- Clear job responsibilities\n\n7. Professional Development\n- Workshops\n- Conferences\n- Online learning resources\n- Certifications support\n\n8. Company Stability\n- Good reputation\n- Financial health\n- Long-term vision\n- Job security\n\n9. Feedback Mechanism\n- Regular performance discussions\n- Open communication channels\n- Constructive feedback\n- Opportunity to share suggestions\n\n10. Inclusive Culture\n- Diversity\n- Equal opportunities\n- Inclusive policies\n- Positive work atmosphere\n\nThese expectations can vary based on industry and specific company culture.",
